                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10114" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-1156</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">248 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“革”故鼎新，卓“尔”不群：歌尔股份的创新管理之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Reform&quot; and &quot;innovation&quot;, &quot;unique&quot; and &quot;unusual&quot;: the road of innovation management of Goer Corporation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈兴述，李欣岚，王振宇，杨文亭，杨舒兰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">歌尔股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">歌尔股份;颠覆式创新；双元创新；消费电子</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Goer Corporation, innovation management; Industrial Ecosystem Restructuring; consumer electronics industry</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球消费电子智能化升级与元宇宙技术发展的背景下，本案例以歌尔股份为研究对象，完整呈现其从传统制造企业向科技创新企业转型的发展历程。案例通过梳理企业“技术研发与客户深度协同”的双轮驱动模式，阐释声学、光学等核心技术体系的形成路径；并重点展示企业在全球化运营中应对研发投入与利润平衡、芯片技术依赖等关键问题的实践过程；同时具体呈现全产业链布局、智能制造升级、工业互联网应用等管理创新举措。通过本案例学习，学生可深入理解颠覆式和双元创新理论在科技企业中的表现，掌握创新管理方法在技术突破与数字化转型中的应用路径，系统认识中国科技企业通过管理创新突破技术壁垒、重构价值链角色的实现机制，为智能硬件领域企业转型升级提供实践范式。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Against the backdrop of the global intelligent upgrade of consumer electronics and the development of metaverse technologies, this case study focuses on Goertek as the subject, presenting a comprehensive account of its transformation from a traditional manufacturing enterprise to a technology-driven innovator. By analyzing the company&#39;s dual-driven model of &quot;technology R&amp;D and deep customer collaboration,&quot; the case elucidates the development path of core technological systems such as acoustics and optics. It highlights the company&#39;s practical approaches to addressing key challenges in global operations, including balancing R&amp;D investment and profitability, and overcoming dependencies on chip technologies. Furthermore, the case details management innovation initiatives such as full-industry-chain layout, smart manufacturing upgrades, and the application of industrial internet. Through this case study, students will gain an in-depth understanding of how disruptive innovation theory manifests in technology enterprises, master the application of innovation management methods in technological breakthroughs and digital transformation, and systematically comprehend the mechanisms by which Chinese tech companies break through technological barriers and redefine their roles in the value chain through management innovation. This provides a practical paradigm for the transformation and upgrading of enterprises in the smart hardware sector.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">颠覆式创新；创新者窘境；双元创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
